==English==

===Noun===
'''byre'''
#(''mostly British'') a [[barn]], especially one used for keeping [[cattle]]

===Quotations===
#*'''1999:''' "The visitors came up the narrow road through the forest from the south; they filled the spare-rooms, they bunked out in cow '''byres''' and barns.  &mdash; ''Stardust'', Neil Gaiman, page 9 (2001 Perennial Edition).
